		<title>狗狗愛亂吃地上東西不是餓！這些「壞習慣」才是真兇</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/06/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e6%84%9b%e4%ba%82%e5%90%83%e5%9c%b0%e4%b8%8a%e6%9d%b1%e8%a5%bf%e4%b8%8d%e6%98%af%e9%a4%93%ef%bc%81%e9%80%99%e4%ba%9b%e3%80%8c%e5%a3%9e%e7%bf%92%e6%85%a3%e3%80%8d%e6%89%8d%e6%98%af/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 06 Oct 2025 04:14:10 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
